des: "When people tell the bartender at Renee's Courtyard Cafe in Santa Monica, 'make me a drink, surprise me,' this is often the one they make. It's fruity, sweet, and tasty."
ins: Fill an old fashioned-type cocktail glass with ice. Pour strawberry vodka, coconut rum, and cranberry juice cocktail over the ice; top off with lemon-lime soda. Squeeze lime into cocktail, stir, and serve.
